                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 534/105.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Stutesman</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">La Paz</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1909-09-16">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 16, 1909</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Reports that Peru and Bolivia have reached an agreement and that protocol is to
                    be signed to-day or to-morrow.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
